Please note: before filling out this template, make sure that your JupyterBook is built and published.

1. Name of the repository: *e.g., DISK-proxyComposite*
2. Repo url: *e.g., https://github.com/khider/DISK-proxyComposite*
3. Url of .config.yml: *e.g.,https://github.com/khider/DISK-proxyComposite/blob/main/proxycomposite/_config.yml*
4. Host for the JupyterBook: *e.g., https://khider.github.io*
5. User: *e.g., khider*
6. Landing suffix (name of the page you want users to land on): *e.g., intro.html*
7. Landing page url: *e.g., https://khider.github.io/DISK-proxyComposite/intro.html*
